div1.p:
He called
Catharine Batford
, who lived near him in Spittlefields;
John Darbyshire
, who had known him near 8 years;
William Grant
, 7;
Mary Darnell
, about 4;
Robert Huddy
, 3; Sarah Bartlet, near 18, and
Thomas Barnet
, 20, who could give but little account of what business he followed, and they never heard any ill of him.
